      "writtenOn": "2021-06-04T20:53:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, fillGlyphs() should work correctly regardless of how the glyph is represented in the typeface.\n\nI suggest all of these Font \"helpers\" to be utilities in case the client wanted to draw things in their own way (e.g. maybe extract the glyph\u0027s path and morph it).",
